Magnificently finished with clever design and minimum effort, these impressive four-bedroom executive residences deliver on every angle. A off the plan choice of luxurious homes is for those who appreciate high-end style with own frontage and low maintenance aspect.

A radiant ground-floor layout is a wonderfully bright open-plan space, as the independent entrance (from York Avenue) leads into a welcoming and light-filled living area. Timber flooring flow into state-of-the-art designer kitchen and dining, which features a large stone bench area to create a social cooking hub. Glass doors open effortlessly onto the private courtyard, requiring a minimum of maintenance is ideal for those get-togethers.

Upstairs, there are three large bedrooms, second Master with walk-in robe & ensuite, others with robes and family bathroom. Downstairs Master boasts a fantastic ensuite and huge walk-in robe.

Designed to the highest modern standards, with a remote garage and external car space, excellent transport links including train & buses to the city and close to parks, Chadstone Shopping Centre, Monash Medical Centre, the Monash Freeway and Huntingdale Golf Club, this superb property will make you the envy and the favorite destination of all your friends.

• Maximum Stamp Duty Saving Currently Apply
• Builder warranty on new builds applies
• Independent Frontage
